name: @fiasco9.0 "MakeShiftVerse"
description:

This ongoing @fiasco9.0 art collection consists mostly of artwork with more digital glitch manipulation & abstract ideas based on a distorted sense of self. For today's piece however, I wanted to dedicate it to the fans of both NFTs & Mechas that Mekan't drive one (badumtss lol). It doesn't matter the reason for not being able to collect the drop, but what I do know is that the MekaVerse nfts look incredibly sick & more than likely, I myself would never be able to get my hands on one or have part of the amazing project T_T. That alone inspired this. Some sort of animated glitch MekaVerse fan art & tribute.

Minting 50/50 editions of this baby..you are able to collect one of them for 0.5 TEZ
